 k because things are about to get poppin’ all season long!\nWhen: Every 
 Thursday from 6 PM - 9 PM on June 4 - July 30\nWhere: Main Street\nCost: F
 ree admission + parking (some activities cost $5-10)\nSchedule of Events\n
 6 PM - 9 PM: Kids’ Activities + DJ Matt\n6:30 PM - 8:30 PM: Bubble Truck
  (glow bubbles for the last 30 minutes!)\n8:30 PM\, 9 PM\, 9:30 PM: SPECTR
 A Laser Light Show\nDon’t forget a swimsuit + towel for the water activi
 ties!\nLet's get poppin' at the Wharf!\nNote: The Wharf will NOT have Beat
 s + Bubbles on July 2\, 16 and 23.\n\n---\n🌐 View original event: https
