 e\nJune 1: The Parent Trap\nJune 8: The Little Rascals\nJune 15: Dennis th
 e Menace\nJune 22: Free Willy\nJune 29: Remember the Titans\nJuly 6: Angel
 s in the Outfield\nJuly 13: Sing 2\nJuly 20: Clifford the Big Red Dog\nJul
 y 27: Migration\nMake The Wharf your Monday movie destination this summer
