DTSTART:20260806T170000
DTEND:20260806T230000
DTSTAMP:20260625T062511Z
UID:gz-28th-annual-jcmf-professional-rodeo-1757825@southbaldwinchamber.com
DESCRIPTION:Description\nThe 28th Annual JCMF Rodeo is returning to Robert
 sdale!\nGet ready for an unforgettable experience at the 28th Annual Profe
 ssional Rodeo\, hosted by the\nJennifer Claire Moore Foundation\n!\nThis y
 ear\, we’re bringing you an action-packed\, family-friendly event filled
  with entertainment for all ages. Get ready for fun for all ages at our Ki
 d's Corral\, happening before the rodeo action kicks off! Stick around for
  the rodeo\, and let your kids join in on the excitement with the calf scr
 amble (for ages 6-12)!\nWith more seating\, delicious concessions\, exciti
 ng vendors\, and plenty of activities\, there's something for everyone.\nS
 chedule of Events\n5:00 PM: Gates Open\n5:30 PM: Kid's Corral\n7:30 PM: Ro
 deo Action\nOur rodeo features livestock and event management from Bo Camp
 bell Rodeo Productions and contestants are affiliated with the Professiona
 l Cowboy Association\, ensuring a high-energy\, jaw-dropping experience th
 at you won’t want to miss.\nBut that's not all!\nWe’re also bringing i
 n a Professional Rodeo Clown to keep the crowd laughing with hilarious ant
 ics. With a perfect mix of humor for both kids and adults\, the rodeo clow
 n ensures there’s never a dull moment! We’ve made sure to include plen
 ty of specialty acts geared toward children\, so the whole family can enjo
 y the day together. Whether you're a rodeo enthusiast or new to the sport\
 , our event promises memories to last a lifetime!\nWith the arena being co
 vered\, this is a rain or shine event. It’s an experience you won’t wa
 nt to miss!\nCheck out our Facebook page!\n\n---\n🌐 View original event
 : https://businesshub.southbaldwinchamber.com/calendar/Details/28th-annual
 -jcmf-professional-rodeo-1757825
LOCATION:19477 Fairground Road\, Robertsdale\,\, AL\, 36567\, United State
 s
END:VEVENT
