UID:gz-community-safety-day-at-owa-parks-resort-1763417@southbaldwinchambe
 r.com
DESCRIPTION:Description\nCommunity Safety Day is coming to Downtown OWA on
  August 22nd!\nIt’s all about celebrating the people and organizations t
 hat keep our community safe and strong! Spend the day meeting local first 
 responders from across the area\, watching K-9 training demonstrations\, a
 nd enjoying a live DJ on OWA Island.\nJoin us for a fun\, feel-good day fo
 r families\, friends\, and neighbors to come together and show appreciatio
 n for the heroes among us!\nCalling all first responders!\nRegister your d
 epartment for the Heroes Hunger Games\, a fast-paced challenge where teams
  race to finish a sub sandwich\, milkshake\, pretzel\, and large soda befo
 re suiting up in full gear. Winning departments take home a station banner
 \, a trophy\, park tickets\, and bragging rights!\nSign Up Your Department
  Today | Learn More About Community Safety Day\n\n---\n🌐 View original 
 event: https://businesshub.southbaldwinchamber.com/calendar/Details/commun
 ity-safety-day-at-owa-parks-resort-1763417
