UID:gz-2026-golf-fore-education-1683374@southbaldwinchamber.com
DESCRIPTION:Description\nThe\nSouth Baldwin Chamber Foundation\nis proud t
 o partner with GlenLakes Golf Club to host the\n6th Annual Golf FORE! Educ
 ation Tournament\non October 2\, 2026\, presented by\nBaldwin EMC\n!\nThe 
 day will begin with a grab-and-go breakfast at The Pub at GlenLakes\, foll
 owed by an 8 AM shotgun start.\nThis year’s tournament will be played as
  a\nfour-man scramble\n. Players will enjoy contests and games along the c
 ourse\, plus a silent auction before and after the tournament.\nA\nfour-pe
 rson team entry is $600\nincludes breakfast\, lunch\, and 2 drinks per pla
 yer. Lunch will be served following the tournament.\nSponsorship Opportuni
 ties:\nWe are currently looking for like-minded businesses to partner with
  us in sponsorship for the Golf FORE! Education Golf Tournament. Sponsorsh
 ip levels and participation range from a $1\,500 award sponsor to a $150 t
 ee sign.\nAdditionally\, we are accepting donations of items for a silent 
 auction.\nAbout the Foundation:\nThe\nSouth Baldwin Chamber Foundation\nsu
 pports 11 public schools in the Foley and Elberta feeder patterns\, along 
 with three private schools in South Baldwin County. Our mission is to enha
 nce lives through programs and partnerships that enrich education\, develo
 p leadership\, and better our community.\n\n---\n🌐 View original event:
  https://businesshub.southbaldwinchamber.com/calendar/Details/2026-golf-fo
 re-education-1683374
LOCATION:GlenLakes Golf Club\, 9530 Clubhouse Dr.\, Foley\,\, AL\, 36535\,
  United States
END:VEVENT
