DTEND:20261107T110000
DTSTAMP:20260625T062511Z
UID:gz-2026-magnolia-run-1682730@southbaldwinchamber.com
DESCRIPTION:Description\nRunners\, walkers\, and those who enjoy the outdo
 ors are sure to have a blast participating in the\nMagnolia Run\n\, presen
 ted by\nBaldwin County Sewer Service\non Saturday\, November 7\, 2026\, in
  Magnolia Springs\, Alabama.\nThe Magnolia Run is a 5K Run\, 5K Walk\, and
  1 Mile Fun Run that welcomes around 300 participants and takes place in M
 agnolia Springs down a beautiful scenic route with majestic oak branch can
 opies overhanging the road\, lovely azaleas\, flowering plants\, and histo
 ric homes. This run is stroller and dog friendly.\nAwards are presented to
  a wide variety of age groups.\nAll runners are welcome to participate in 
 post-race activities – lively DJ music\, delicious food provided by Jess
 e's Restaurant\, beverages\, and door prizes!\nThis race is USATF certifie
 d\, certificate number AL19018JE\, and begins and ends at Jesse's Restaura
 nt in Magnolia Springs.\nPacket pick up will be Saturday\, October 31 from
  9 AM - 2 PM at the South Baldwin Chamber of Commerce or on Saturday\, Nov
 ember 7 from 6:30 AM - 7:30 AM at the Magnolia Springs Community Hall.\n\n
 ---\n🌐 View original event: https://businesshub.southbaldwinchamber.com
 /calendar/Details/2026-magnolia-run-1682730
LOCATION:Address\, 14770 Oak Street\, Magnolia Springs\,\, AL\, 36555\, Un
 ited States
END:VEVENT
