 he Foley Lions Club. It’s a\nnon-competitive ride that begins at the Fol
 ey Sports Complex:\nno racing\, just a great day in beautiful Baldwin Coun
 ty with friends\, neighbors\, and fellow supporters. E-bikes are welcome!\
 nYour entry fee includes a commemorative T-shirt. Contact us for sponsorsh
 ip opportunities!\nChoose from two routes: a 40-mile ride or a 23-mile par
 tial route. Convenient rest stations will be provided along both routes. O
 n-site check-in begins at 7:30 AM. Plenty of parking is available at the s
 ports complex.\nWe appreciate your support of the\nFoley Lions Club\nand l
 ook forward to seeing you there!\nPlease note that routes shown on the reg
 istration site may change slightly between now and November 14.\nRegister 
 today!\n\n---\n🌐 View original event: https://businesshub.southbaldwinc
