DESCRIPTION:Description\nReady your maps and sharpen your skills—it’s 
 time to blaze the trail for a great cause.\nAttention\, Scouts! Gather you
 r patrol and embark on an epic summer adventure every Wednesday at The Wha
 rf.\nYour mission? To navigate the great\nPepsi Summer Adventure Quest\n!\
 nStart your journey by reporting to the Pepsi Outpost\, where you'll recei
 ve your official adventure map. Then\, set out on a thrilling scavenger hu
 nt\, following the trail to uncover hidden waypoints and complete your que
 st. Once you've checked off every challenge\, return to Base Camp where "X
 " marks the spot to claim your well-earned reward! After your adventure\, 
 stick around to enjoy music from DJ Matt\, and witness the SPECTRA Laser L
 ight Experience.\nWhen: Every Wednesday from 6 PM - 9 PM from June 3 - Jul
 y 29\nWhere: Palms Plaza\nCost: Free admission + parking (some activities 
 $5-10)\nSchedule of Events\n6 PM - 9 PM: Pepsi Summer Adventure Quest\n8:3
 0 PM\, 9 PM\, 9:30 PM: SPECTRA Laser Light Experience\nFor the first 500 c
 hildren to complete the hunt\, The Wharf’s Anchor Campaign will make a s
 pecial $5 donation in the child’s honor to the Alabama Credit Union’s 
 Secret Meals for Hungry Children program\, helping provide meals to kids i
 n need. We appreciate your support!\nNote: There will be no Pepsi Summer A
 dventure Quest on July 15\nLearn more about the Pepsi Summer Adventure Que
 st!\n\n---\n🌐 View original event: https://businesshub.southbaldwincham
