BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:🛥️ The Salty Shuffle Charity Boat Poker Cruise
DTSTART:20260613T100000
DTEND:20260613T180000
DTSTAMP:20260625T062511Z
UID:gz-the-salty-shuffle-charity-boat-poker-cruise-1736206@southbaldwincha
 mber.com
DESCRIPTION:Description\nLegendary Marina\, Dockside Guide\, and The Sea G
 lass Initiative are back and ready to make waves at the 2nd Annual Salty S
 huffle Poker Cruise!\nJoin us for another incredible\, family-friendly day
  on the water filled with adventure\, community spirit\, and a shared miss
 ion to give back.\nOnce registered\, participants will navigate the scenic
  Intracoastal Waterway (ICW)\, visiting our designated waterfront stops. T
 his year\, it’s all about the journey! At each official stop\, you’ll 
 check in to build your poker hand for the big reveal. Enjoy the local flav
 or at each location and support our partners by grabbing a snack or a refr
 eshment as you cruise through the route.\nThe adventure leads back to the 
 Legendary Marina in Gulf Shores for our high-energy wrap-up party starting
  at 4:00PM. This is where the tension builds as\nplayers reveal their han
 ds to see who will be crowned this year’s poker champion!\nThe fun doesn
 't stop at the docks. Our wrap-up party features:\nInteractive Games: Test
  your luck with fan favorites like Plinko.\nSilent Auction: Bid on amazing
  items & experiences.\nEntertainment: Enjoy delicious food\, music\, & the
  best company on the coast.\nEvery registration and contribution directly 
 benefits The Sea Glass Initiative.\nYour support helps us provide vital re
 sources and solutions to end housing insecurity in our community.\nJoin us
  for an unforgettable day of boating\, bonding\, and making a real differe
 nce!\nLearn more & grab your tickets today!\n\n---\n🌐 View original eve
 nt: https://businesshub.southbaldwinchamber.com/calendar/Details/the-salty
 -shuffle-charity-boat-poker-cruise-1736206
LOCATION:Legendary Marine & Yacht Club\, 335 Waterway Boulevard\, Gulf Sho
 res\,\, AL\, 36542\, United States
END:VEVENT
